Oh sorry guys I was wrong. This is still synchronous. Here's an asynchronous way of calling N functions in a row:<p><pre><code>  var callback = Pie.callback(3, function() { 
  // do stuff
  }); // makes a function that counts down from 3 and when it reaches 0 calls that inner function

  async_thing(1, "foo", callback);

  some_other_async_thing(2, callback);
  third_thing(2, callback);</code></pre>
